{"id":476915,"date":[{"year":1966,"month":6,"day":30}],"page":"4","source":"","region":"","masthead":"","special_issue":"笔会","column":"工农兵纪念“七一”诗画选,歌唱共产党　歌唱毛主席","genre":"","count":"171","ytitle":"","mtitle":"听了毛主席的话","ftitle":"","authors":["张呈富"],"text":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"上海汽轮机厂　张呈富"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"听了毛主席的话，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"干起活来劲头大，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"造出汽轮机千万台，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"电火闪闪照天下。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"听了毛主席的话，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"自力更生有办法，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"雄姿焕发闹赶超，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"红旗专往高峰插。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"听了毛主席的话，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"能辨毒草和香花，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"金猴奋起千钧棒，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"牛鬼蛇神见咱怕。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"听了毛主席的话，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"党说干啥就干啥，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"三大革命当先锋，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"颗颗红心放光华。"}]}